                            The portal ensures accessibility across various devices, including desktops, tablets, and smartphones, delivering a consistent user experience.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Backend Development:</strong> Built with ASP.NET and C#, the backend provides a scalable and maintainable structure to handle complex workflows and business logic seamlessly.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Database:</strong> SQL Server was employed to securely store and manage employee profiles, task assignments, attendance records, and performance reviews.
