                <div class="mb-3">
                    <h4 class="section-title">Core Features</h4>
                    <ul class="list-group">
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Employee Profiles:</strong> Comprehensive profiles with personal and professional details, including contact information, job roles, and employment history.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Leave Management:</strong> Streamlines leave application and approval processes with real-time status updates for employees and managers.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Task Assignment:</strong> Allows managers to assign and track tasks efficiently, ensuring clarity and accountability in task management.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Document Sharing:</strong> Facilitates secure sharing of company policies, forms, and other important documents with employees.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>HR Notifications:</strong> Automates HR notifications for announcements, policy updates, and event reminders, keeping employees informed and engaged.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <h4 class="section-title">Security Measures</h4>
                    <ul class="list-group">
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Role-Based Access Control:</strong> Implements secure access protocols to ensure that sensitive data is accessible only to authorized personnel, such as administrators and managers.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Data Encryption:</strong> Encrypts sensitive employee data to safeguard against unauthorized access and data breaches.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Audit Trails:</strong> Maintains detailed logs of system activities to ensure transparency and accountability.
                        </li>
